{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"7f087dcff59d92b6a021685733eb4f1cbab040993e603cfc9c815e36813ce5af","slug":"seismology.seismic-wave","location":"/seismology/seismic-wave.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"地震波","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/blob/main/source/seismology/seismic-wave.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/edit/main/source/seismology/seismic-wave.md","thumbnail":"/seismology101/build/body-wave-propagatio-940784b8de26bb90ee7876d582f8c342.jpg","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"seismic-wave.md","url":"/seismology101/build/seismic-wave-b75c7898bff6fc9f09582818aa730f7f.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"本节贡献者: {{ 姚家园 }}、{{ 田冬冬 }}","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"QagJkxojs3"}],"key":"HEY2khfmC0"}],"key":"HklOEjfs3e"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近更新日期: 2022-11-12","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"WO6C6qkss7"}],"key":"cDZgiKHAoj"}],"key":"kpYEfUsp7i"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"预计阅读时间: 20 分钟","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"k3MfR1G8gm"}],"key":"YusfOaBiKg"}],"key":"VhgulY6fOH"}],"key":"cjUchz70qs"},{"type":"thematicBreak","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"ZPRPmIJsWV"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"震源激发的机械振动以地震波的形式在地球内部传播。地震波分为体波（body wave）\n和面波（surface wave）两种类型。体波是指在地球内部传播的波，而面波是指在地球表面\n附近传播的波。本节将介绍最基础的地震波理论。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"a0JlxwE6ZU"}],"key":"sL8ZCu9AI8"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"体波","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"j8Bpsu3hXD"}],"identifier":"id","label":"体波","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"GUZKJS8AhD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"体波分为 P 波（P-wave）和 S 波（S-wave）两种。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"CpG5tJfRHx"}],"key":"dPRmh0myJo"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从传播速度的角度看，P 波比 S 波传播速度快。因而 P 波总是最先到达观测者所在的位置，\nS 波则在 P 波后到达。因而，P 波和 S 波也分别被称为 ","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"f6OBZoYSkF"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"p","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"A7lriZVs4f"}],"key":"pNLUC1X1p4"},{"type":"text","value":"rimary wave 和 ","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"XYCXt0I4I4"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"s","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"KK5tFyIteS"}],"key":"Lz1GOf4nY5"},{"type":"text","value":"econdary wave。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"E5Iidy6D4G"}],"key":"voag2CN5g5"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从物理属性上来说，P 波是一种纵波（longitudinal wave），P 波在介质中传播时，介质的\n运动方向与波传播的方向相同或相反，介质交替压缩和膨胀导致介质的体积发生变化（如下图所示），\n因而 P 波也称为压缩波（com","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"kAm2q2ztk5"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"p","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"vnNZq18MvU"}],"key":"zkQz2w1kVA"},{"type":"text","value":"ressional wave）。S 波是一种横波（transverse wave），\nS 波在介质中传播时，介质的运动方向与波传播的方向垂直，会造成介质的剪切变形，但\n不改变介质的体积（如下图示），因而 S 波也称为剪切波（","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"TvEIvVva1B"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"s","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"s5RoFK25wH"}],"key":"Ez6bSk6POg"},{"type":"text","value":"hear wave）。","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"LDsFdDefgH"}],"key":"agS7txy97v"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"事实上，地震学家首先根据波到达的先后顺序将两种波命名为 primary wave 和 secondary wave，\n并简称为 P-wave 和 S-wave，最后在进一步理解了两种地震波的物理属性后，才分别\n将其称为 com","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"NnrRIgdqa7"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"p","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"KI79TJzcPK"}],"key":"m0Ev6bwanf"},{"type":"text","value":"ressional wave 和 ","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"VJ5jsIAQeN"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"s","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"ir4PCsmQJ2"}],"key":"zPm6H7GV6W"},{"type":"text","value":"hear wave。","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"isdaLT6qKW"}],"key":"uNnlkSvtvk"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/seismology101/build/body-wave-propagatio-940784b8de26bb90ee7876d582f8c342.jpg","alt":"\"体波的介质运动方向以及波传播方向\"","width":"80%","align":"center","key":"bcxzWPjbuf","urlSource":"body-wave-propagation.jpg"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"体波的介质运动方向以及波传播方向。引自《","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"lRpyK4jcAi"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.cambridge.org/us/academic/subjects/earth-and-environmental-science/solid-earth-geophysics/introduction-seismology-3rd-edition?format=HB&isbn=9781316635742","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Introduction to Seismology","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"hx1X4VYHIV"}],"urlSource":"https://www.cambridge.org/us/academic/subjects/earth-and-environmental-science/solid-earth-geophysics/introduction-seismology-3rd-edition?format=HB&isbn=9781316635742","key":"xtGcosF0D3"},{"type":"text","value":"》（第三版）图 3.2。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"kwtrldtZNi"}],"key":"N7zIMvBtnX"}],"key":"xIMKYJZDA1"}],"enumerator":"1","key":"lUJm6HM9d2"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"面波","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"WOfaeFH8ea"}],"identifier":"id","label":"面波","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"Zg3PMYCbSD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"沿着地球表面附近传播的面波也有两种，即瑞利波（Rayleigh wave）和勒夫波（Love wave）。\nRayleigh 波在地表传播时，介质的运动既有与波传播方向相同或相反的分量，又有与波传播方向垂直\n的分量（如下图示）。Love 波在地表传播时，介质的运动方向与波传播方向垂直（如下图示）。\n面波的振幅随着深度增加会剧烈减少。","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"is7pMZ4RfC"}],"key":"bT8FzA7fJy"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/seismology101/build/surface-wave-propaga-2f7ec05bb07ba7917c8a60e040d8cd8a.jpg","alt":"\"面波的介质运动方向以及波传播方向\"","width":"50%","align":"center","key":"Uqd8AFDZzw","urlSource":"surface-wave-propagation.jpg"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基阶 Love 波（上）和 Rayleigh 波（下）的介质运动方向（假设面波沿着页面从左向右传播）。\n引自《","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"f1GzFGVrSZ"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.cambridge.org/us/academic/subjects/earth-and-environmental-science/solid-earth-geophysics/introduction-seismology-3rd-edition?format=HB&isbn=9781316635742","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Introduction to Seismology","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"ZULN4pT1xk"}],"urlSource":"https://www.cambridge.org/us/academic/subjects/earth-and-environmental-science/solid-earth-geophysics/introduction-seismology-3rd-edition?format=HB&isbn=9781316635742","key":"wWEf6y3HMM"},{"type":"text","value":"》（第三版）图 8.5。","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"eHGHLSTpy7"}],"key":"UT3lSbKVFj"}],"key":"ABNPRH6ObD"}],"enumerator":"2","key":"hHOiV1dc3H"}],"key":"zgHJlI9nva"}],"key":"qxG